# Keep docker build contexts small and avoid copying pnpm symlinked node_modules
# (which point outside the build context and would break COPY). Image deps are
# installed inside the Dockerfile instead.
node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
tests/e2e/test-results
deploy/kind/web-console/dist
deploy/kind/.uiout
deploy/kind/credentials.env
deploy/kind/tls
*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log

# Release image (deploy/release/web-console.Dockerfile) copies the CI-built web-console SPA
# bundle, which lives under a dist/ dir excluded by **/dist above. Re-include just that bundle
# (built by the release-images workflow's `vite build` step) so the nginx release image can serve
# it. Harmless for other builds: the dir only exists in the web-console release job.
!apps/web-console/dist
!apps/web-console/dist/**
